OL,3,C'Voiceless for so many years': Appeal
OL,4,Cfor information over 40 years after
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FDuring the attack, the milk float
OL,8,Fcollided with a concrete lamp post on
OL,9,Fthe Antrim Road at its junction with
OL,10,FDuncairn Avenue, opposite the New
OL,11,FLodge Road.
OL,13,FDesmond died of his injuries three
OL,14,Fdays after the incident, while Mr
OL,15,FGuiney died the day after his son's
OL,16,Ffuneral on May 13.
OL,18,FFollowing a request from the Guiney
OL,19,Ffamily, the Commission is now
OL,20,Fappealing for witnesses to come
OL,21,Fforward.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
