OL,3,C'Voiceless for so many years': Appeal
OL,4,Cfor information over 40 years after
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FJoanne Dorrian from the South East
OL,8,FFermanagh Foundation, a victims and
OL,9,Fsurvivors group, said: "We support a
OL,10,Fbrother and sister of the Guiney
OL,11,Ffamily, but there are other members of
OL,12,Fthe family who have died before their
OL,13,Ftime with suffering from a broken
OL,14,Fheart.
OL,16,F"There's Julie who died in 2014, who
OL,17,Fnever got over the loss of her father
OL,18,Fand her brother, and Roberta, who died
OL,19,Fin 2021, and again just lived a life
OL,20,Fof trauma when she lost her husband
OL,21,Fand her son.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
