OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,F"That's really the heart of this
OL,8,Fmessage today - the Guiney family will
OL,9,Fcontinue to ask for answers.
OL,11,F"They've been voiceless for so many
OL,12,Fyears, so those bigger questions of
OL,13,Fwho threw the missiles, who threw the
OL,14,Fbricks at the van, all of those
OL,15,Fquestions are still as relevant as
OL,16,Fthey were on day one, and those are
OL,17,Fthe answers that they deserve."
OL,19,FAssistant commissioner Amanda Logan is
OL,20,Furging anyone with information to come
OL,21,Fforward to help the Guiney family.
