OL,7,F"All information will be treated in
OL,8,Fthe strictest confidence."
OL,10,FShe added: "The Guiney family has
OL,11,Fwaited more than four decades to learn
OL,12,Fthe truth of what happened that day.
OL,14,F"At the Commission we will help them
OL,15,Fin every way we can, and I appeal to
OL,16,Fthe public to assist us in this work."
OL,18,FThe ICRIR said its witness appeal will
OL,19,Finvolve distributing posters and an
OL,20,Forganised leaflet drop in the area
OL,21,Frelating to the investigation.
